{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-js","path":"/blog/perpl","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"fields":{"slug":"perpl"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Human Resource Management System, Performance Plus","author":"Minkyoung Lee, The Plus team","date":"December 4th, 2018","hero_image":{"childImageSharp":{"fluid":{"base64":"data:image/jpeg;base64,","aspectRatio":1.3345195729537367,"src":"/static/5e0ba5612572c67fc375ae64ad92424c/398d8/perpl-1.jpg","srcSet":"/static/5e0ba5612572c67fc375ae64ad92424c/8def4/perpl-1.jpg 375w,\n/static/5e0ba5612572c67fc375ae64ad92424c/35c3d/perpl-1.jpg 750w,\n/static/5e0ba5612572c67fc375ae64ad92424c/398d8/perpl-1.jpg 1500w,\n/static/5e0ba5612572c67fc375ae64ad92424c/ea0f8/perpl-1.jpg 1984w","sizes":"(max-width: 1500px) 100vw, 1500px"}}}},"html":"<div class=\"iframe-container\">\n<iframe class=\"responsive-iframe\" src=\"https://player.vimeo.com/video/502138126\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n</div>\n<p>It is difficult to manage team members' goals and progress of working. And they try to find a basis and records of working when evaluating employees. We developed Performance Plus, a performance management system to solve these issues. </p>\n<ul>\n<li>Client | HCG</li>\n<li>Cowork with | Junwon Lee (pusblisher), Dongouk Lee (developer), Youngjae Baek (developer), Seunghee Shin (developer), Jihoon Jeon (developer), Kyungkyu Lee (developer)</li>\n<li>Duration | Nov 2017 - Jun 2020 (launched Dec 2018)</li>\n<li>Responsibility | project management, service planning, overall UX/UI design, wireframe, interaction design, web publishing </li>\n<li>Tools | Sketch, After Effects, Illustrator, Photoshop</li>\n</ul>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1000px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 57.199999999999996%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"perpl explain 1\"\n        title=\"perpl explain 1\"\n        src=\"/static/105acd6fc45f09972529126c99a98cd9/a2510/perpl-explain-1.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/105acd6fc45f09972529126c99a98cd9/0479a/perpl-explain-1.jpg 250w,\n/static/105acd6fc45f09972529126c99a98cd9/41099/perpl-explain-1.jpg 500w,\n/static/105acd6fc45f09972529126c99a98cd9/a2510/perpl-explain-1.jpg 1000w,\n/static/105acd6fc45f09972529126c99a98cd9/c58a3/perpl-explain-1.jpg 1500w,\n/static/105acd6fc45f09972529126c99a98cd9/3acf0/perpl-explain-1.jpg 2000w,\n/static/105acd6fc45f09972529126c99a98cd9/97894/perpl-explain-1.jpg 2501w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span>\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1000px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 33.199999999999996%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"perpl explain 2\"\n        title=\"perpl explain 2\"\n        src=\"/static/be96fe529335ae2f41ee51a34ec50274/a2510/perpl-explain-2.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/be96fe529335ae2f41ee51a34ec50274/0479a/perpl-explain-2.jpg 250w,\n/static/be96fe529335ae2f41ee51a34ec50274/41099/perpl-explain-2.jpg 500w,\n/static/be96fe529335ae2f41ee51a34ec50274/a2510/perpl-explain-2.jpg 1000w,\n/static/be96fe529335ae2f41ee51a34ec50274/c58a3/perpl-explain-2.jpg 1500w,\n/static/be96fe529335ae2f41ee51a34ec50274/3acf0/perpl-explain-2.jpg 2000w,\n/static/be96fe529335ae2f41ee51a34ec50274/97894/perpl-explain-2.jpg 2501w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p>With Performance Plus, 1) users can record and share their goals, degree of achievements and status of progress with their team or company. It promotes members to find tasks proactively. 2) Members can see what others are doing and send feedback about their works. 3) All data is stored in the cloud system and accumulated data is present in visualizations. At company's the evaluation period, managers can overview user's works through the represented data.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1000px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 75.99999999999999%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"perpl 2\"\n        title=\"perpl 2\"\n        src=\"/static/f022ea1e739b857ed146e8e87f03d5e0/a2510/perpl-2.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/f022ea1e739b857ed146e8e87f03d5e0/0479a/perpl-2.jpg 250w,\n/static/f022ea1e739b857ed146e8e87f03d5e0/41099/perpl-2.jpg 500w,\n/static/f022ea1e739b857ed146e8e87f03d5e0/a2510/perpl-2.jpg 1000w,\n/static/f022ea1e739b857ed146e8e87f03d5e0/c58a3/perpl-2.jpg 1500w,\n/static/f022ea1e739b857ed146e8e87f03d5e0/977d5/perpl-2.jpg 1701w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p><b>Main screen of Performance Plus</b></p>\n<p>The circle graph shows overall progress of goals and the line graph indicates the progress of the individual goals. Depending on the progress of the individual goals, user can set its status into three conditions; 'in progress', 'delay' and 'help'.</p>\n<p>The second column shows accumulated received badges (a symbolic image of the values that are important to the company) of the user. It also shows feedbacks user received recently. </p>\n<p>The last column shows up coming deadlines or status of user's collaborated works and users can access to the working board that is in the collaboration menu through it.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1000px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 68.39999999999999%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"perpl wireframe 1\"\n        title=\"perpl wireframe 1\"\n        src=\"/static/df22e82cc8c7ec92427ee8b03d9f7029/a2510/perpl-wireframe-1.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/df22e82cc8c7ec92427ee8b03d9f7029/0479a/perpl-wireframe-1.jpg 250w,\n/static/df22e82cc8c7ec92427ee8b03d9f7029/41099/perpl-wireframe-1.jpg 500w,\n/static/df22e82cc8c7ec92427ee8b03d9f7029/a2510/perpl-wireframe-1.jpg 1000w,\n/static/df22e82cc8c7ec92427ee8b03d9f7029/c58a3/perpl-wireframe-1.jpg 1500w,\n/static/df22e82cc8c7ec92427ee8b03d9f7029/77eac/perpl-wireframe-1.jpg 1979w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p><b>Wirefreame and system planning</b></p>\n<p>To work in an agile way, I developed UI design and made wireframes at the same time. This is the initial design of the Performance Plus in 2017. </p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1000px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 67.60000000000001%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"perpl wireframe 2\"\n        title=\"perpl wireframe 2\"\n        src=\"/static/b664b7e160b492c37eb9ff8c83ba8c32/a2510/perpl-wireframe-2.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/b664b7e160b492c37eb9ff8c83ba8c32/0479a/perpl-wireframe-2.jpg 250w,\n/static/b664b7e160b492c37eb9ff8c83ba8c32/41099/perpl-wireframe-2.jpg 500w,\n/static/b664b7e160b492c37eb9ff8c83ba8c32/a2510/perpl-wireframe-2.jpg 1000w,\n/static/b664b7e160b492c37eb9ff8c83ba8c32/c58a3/perpl-wireframe-2.jpg 1500w,\n/static/b664b7e160b492c37eb9ff8c83ba8c32/8307e/perpl-wireframe-2.jpg 1667w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span>\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1000px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 170.4%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"perpl wireframe 3\"\n        title=\"perpl wireframe 3\"\n        src=\"/static/22552df5f394b5481f3796ac18fffd65/a2510/perpl-wireframe-3.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/22552df5f394b5481f3796ac18fffd65/0479a/perpl-wireframe-3.jpg 250w,\n/static/22552df5f394b5481f3796ac18fffd65/41099/perpl-wireframe-3.jpg 500w,\n/static/22552df5f394b5481f3796ac18fffd65/a2510/perpl-wireframe-3.jpg 1000w,\n/static/22552df5f394b5481f3796ac18fffd65/af5f6/perpl-wireframe-3.jpg 1166w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p>As inventing company's UI system and launching more new services, I updated UI design for web and mobile according to the established UI system. </p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1000px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 108%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"perpl goal 3\"\n        title=\"perpl goal 3\"\n        src=\"/static/05d5ebd2da4d373079e308ff53a8832a/a2510/perpl-goal-3.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/05d5ebd2da4d373079e308ff53a8832a/0479a/perpl-goal-3.jpg 250w,\n/static/05d5ebd2da4d373079e308ff53a8832a/41099/perpl-goal-3.jpg 500w,\n/static/05d5ebd2da4d373079e308ff53a8832a/a2510/perpl-goal-3.jpg 1000w,\n/static/05d5ebd2da4d373079e308ff53a8832a/c58a3/perpl-goal-3.jpg 1500w,\n/static/05d5ebd2da4d373079e308ff53a8832a/d8f2d/perpl-goal-3.jpg 1756w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p><b>My goals (beneath)</b></p>\n<p>Users can set their task and share it with others by graphs. </p>\n<p><b>Teammates' goals (above)</b></p>\n<p>Users can view their team members' works easily. Therefore, they can easily understand what other people are working on and can help them.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1000px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 86.80000000000001%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"perpl goal 4\"\n        title=\"perpl goal 4\"\n        src=\"/static/caab6722664caa22a69cd1408ec6931e/a2510/perpl-goal-4.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/caab6722664caa22a69cd1408ec6931e/0479a/perpl-goal-4.jpg 250w,\n/static/caab6722664caa22a69cd1408ec6931e/41099/perpl-goal-4.jpg 500w,\n/static/caab6722664caa22a69cd1408ec6931e/a2510/perpl-goal-4.jpg 1000w,\n/static/caab6722664caa22a69cd1408ec6931e/58b23/perpl-goal-4.jpg 1417w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p><b>Goal treemap</b></p>\n<p>Users can view those works in a treemap which is convenient to view which works are related. </p>\n<div class=\"iframe-container\">\n<iframe class=\"responsive-iframe\" src=\"https://player.vimeo.com/video/502157961\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n</div>\n<p><b>Interaction of check-in and giving feedback</b></p>\n<p>This video shows how users can check-in to their goal (record the progress of the work). The checked-in graph bar are shown as slashed lines when it is not confirmed by their manager (it is to prevent misuse and abuse of the system). </p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1000px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 89.60000000000001%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"perpl fb 3\"\n        title=\"perpl fb 3\"\n        src=\"/static/eeeeac6c98e1cfa69d4f424763ada642/a2510/perpl-fb-3.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/eeeeac6c98e1cfa69d4f424763ada642/0479a/perpl-fb-3.jpg 250w,\n/static/eeeeac6c98e1cfa69d4f424763ada642/41099/perpl-fb-3.jpg 500w,\n/static/eeeeac6c98e1cfa69d4f424763ada642/a2510/perpl-fb-3.jpg 1000w,\n/static/eeeeac6c98e1cfa69d4f424763ada642/58b23/perpl-fb-3.jpg 1417w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p><b>Mobile screen of sending feedback</b></p>\n<p>Not only sending a message, users can send badges to appreicate others work. </p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1000px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 114.39999999999999%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"perpl coll 2\"\n        title=\"perpl coll 2\"\n        src=\"/static/b5ea36e82415d64fcb27671346d76b35/a2510/perpl-coll-2.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/b5ea36e82415d64fcb27671346d76b35/0479a/perpl-coll-2.jpg 250w,\n/static/b5ea36e82415d64fcb27671346d76b35/41099/perpl-coll-2.jpg 500w,\n/static/b5ea36e82415d64fcb27671346d76b35/a2510/perpl-coll-2.jpg 1000w,\n/static/b5ea36e82415d64fcb27671346d76b35/c58a3/perpl-coll-2.jpg 1500w,\n/static/b5ea36e82415d64fcb27671346d76b35/3acf0/perpl-coll-2.jpg 2000w,\n/static/b5ea36e82415d64fcb27671346d76b35/93992/perpl-coll-2.jpg 2088w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p><b>Work board main page (beneath)</b></p>\n<p>The collaboration menu is a function that helps you to work with others. You can manage tasks by grouping them by category using the blue tab bar.</p>\n<p><b>Work board detail page (above)</b></p>\n<p>It contains main information about the collaboration. Users can create checklists, share files, and leave comments work processes with others. Each collaration board can be connected to team or personal goals.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1000px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 85.6%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"perpl review 3\"\n        title=\"perpl review 3\"\n        src=\"/static/93044c15b2c44307d0d0d1edf172fbad/a2510/perpl-review-3.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/93044c15b2c44307d0d0d1edf172fbad/0479a/perpl-review-3.jpg 250w,\n/static/93044c15b2c44307d0d0d1edf172fbad/41099/perpl-review-3.jpg 500w,\n/static/93044c15b2c44307d0d0d1edf172fbad/a2510/perpl-review-3.jpg 1000w,\n/static/93044c15b2c44307d0d0d1edf172fbad/c58a3/perpl-review-3.jpg 1500w,\n/static/93044c15b2c44307d0d0d1edf172fbad/977d5/perpl-review-3.jpg 1701w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span>\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1000px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 85.6%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"perpl review 2\"\n        title=\"perpl review 2\"\n        src=\"/static/2ef367b0aae21b9b1353c13ba9e87ddb/a2510/perpl-review-2.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/2ef367b0aae21b9b1353c13ba9e87ddb/0479a/perpl-review-2.jpg 250w,\n/static/2ef367b0aae21b9b1353c13ba9e87ddb/41099/perpl-review-2.jpg 500w,\n/static/2ef367b0aae21b9b1353c13ba9e87ddb/a2510/perpl-review-2.jpg 1000w,\n/static/2ef367b0aae21b9b1353c13ba9e87ddb/c58a3/perpl-review-2.jpg 1500w,\n/static/2ef367b0aae21b9b1353c13ba9e87ddb/977d5/perpl-review-2.jpg 1701w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p><b>Review, data visualization of feedbacks and goals</b></p>\n<p>Review page is for the evaluation of members in a period. Reviewers can overview members' performance and activities by visualization based on their accumulated data of Goal, Feedback, Collaboration menu. And also each of members can evaluate themselves by reviewing the visualization and comments of the reviewer.</p>\n<div class=\"iframe-container\">\n<iframe class=\"responsive-iframe\" src=\"https://player.vimeo.com/video/502156404\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n</div>\n<p>The status in the main review page, 1) performance 2) promotion potential 3) risk of turnover 4) competence of the member are only exposure to the reviwer. The right window shows feedbacks and comments the subject received. Reviewer and users can answer the questions and write reviews by referencing the visualization. </p>"}},"pageContext":{"slug":"perpl"}},"staticQueryHashes":["2708967481","3255264069"]}